songs.title: Main Hoon Jhoom Jhoom Jhumroo
songs.comments: From the K.S. Pictures film, "Jhumroo" (1961)Kumar's sublime levity obscured the depth of this Bollywood actor, writer, director, composer and producer.  He's best remembered as one of the big playback singers, whose trademark yodelling assured him an honourable place in yodelling pantheon.  Kumar had no professional vocal training - he just winged it, lending his yodelling an untutored abandon and avian robustness, as he mixed odd babbling jazz-scat, bird calls and Western-style yodel flourishes into the rhythms.
